author = "Abbas Ali Mansour and Nassar T.Y. Alibrahim and Haider A. Alidrisi and Ali H. Alhamza and Ammar M. Almomin and Ibrahim Abbood Zaboon and Muayad Baheer Kadhim and Rudha Naser Hussein and Hussein Ali Nwayyir and Adel Gassab Mohammed and Dheyaa K.J. Al-Waeli and Ibrahim Hani Hussein",
